      <title>解决Hugo字数统计不正确</title>
      <link>https://ronin-zc.com/posts/%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3hugo%E5%AD%97%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8D%E6%AD%A3%E7%A1%AE/</link>
